trans-unit.source: Defines the contract that ASP.NET implements to synchronously process HTTP Web requests using custom HTTP handlers.
trans-unit.target: Definerer kontrakten som implementerer ASP.NET for å behandle synkront HTTP Web-forespørsler ved hjelp av egendefinert HTTP-behandlingsprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: You can write custom HTTP handlers to process specific, predefined types of HTTP requests in any Common Language Specification (CLS) compliant language.
trans-unit.target: Du kan skrive egendefinert HTTP-behandlingsprogrammer for å behandle bestemt, forhåndsdefinerte typer HTTP-forespørsler i noe samsvar språk Common Language spesifikasjonen (CLS).

trans-unit.source: Executable code defined in the `HttpHandler` classes, rather than conventional ASP or ASP.NET Web pages, responds to these specific requests.
trans-unit.target: Kjørbar kode som er definert i den `HttpHandler` klasser, i stedet for konvensjonelt ASP eller ASP.NET Web pages, svarer på disse bestemte forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: HTTP handlers give you a means of interacting with the low-level request and response services of the IIS Web server and provide functionality much like ISAPI extensions but with a simpler programming model.
trans-unit.target: HTTP-behandlingsprogrammer gir deg publikasjonens samhandling med lavt nivå forespørselen og svar-tjenester for IIS-nettserveren, og angi funksjonalitet mye som ISAPI-utvidelser, men med en enklere programming modell.

trans-unit.source: If your handler will access session state values, it must implement the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.IRequiresSessionState> interface (a marker interface with no methods).
trans-unit.target: Hvis behandlingsprogrammet tilgang økten tilstand verdier, må den implementere den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.IRequiresSessionState>grensesnittet (et merke grensesnitt med ingen metoder).</xref:System.Web.SessionState.IRequiresSessionState>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether another request can use the <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om en ny forespørsel kan bruke den <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: You explicitly set the IsReusable property to `true` or `false` by code you provide that overrides the IsReusable property accessor (getter).
trans-unit.target: Du har angitt IsReusable-egenskapen `true` eller `false` av en kode du oppgi som overstyrer IsReusable Egenskapsaksessor (getter).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"></xref> instance is reusable; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"> </xref> forekomsten er gjenbrukbart; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Enables processing of HTTP Web requests by a custom <xref uid="langword_csharp_HttpHandler" name="HttpHandler" href=""></xref> that implements the <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer behandling av HTTP-forespørsler med en egendefinert <xref uid="langword_csharp_HttpHandler" name="HttpHandler" href=""> </xref> som implementerer den <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: Place your custom `HttpHandler` code in the ProcessRequest virtual method, as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: Plasser egendefinert `HttpHandler` code i OneNote.ashx virtuelle metoden, som vist i eksemplet nedenfor.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> object that provides references to the intrinsic server objects (for example, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Request" name="Request" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Response" name="Response" href=""></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Session" name="Session" href=""></xref>, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_Server" name="Server" href=""></xref>) used to service HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> objekt som inneholder referanser til de innebygde serverobjektene (for eksempel <xref uid="langword_csharp_Request" name="Request" href=""> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Response" name="Response" href=""> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Session" name="Session" href=""> </xref>, og <xref uid="langword_csharp_Server" name="Server" href=""> </xref>) brukes til å behandle HTTP-forespørsler.
